text: Share 155 shares Miley wore a colorful floral dress, paired with thigh-high boots, and candy necklaces that she draped around her neck and her tied-up ponytail. The singer appeared to be in town shooting the new Bravo television series, Cyrus Vs Cyrus, which will star 29-year-old Brandi and their 57-year-old mom, Tish. Sisters! The 24-year-old star shared a sweet snap with her 27-year-old sister, Brandi, who was in town shooting her Bravo reality show - Cyrus Vs Cyrus - starring her and mom, Tish Cyrus Sibling love! The Party In The USA singer enjoyed her family reunion; here she is posing with 22-year-old brother Braison (far left) and 27-year-old Trace (far right) The mother-daughter duo will battle to win clients redecorating their homes in Nashville, with the clients choosing one of the plans to enact. A spokesperson said of the show earlier: 'Tish and Brandi have a wonderful, funny, modern mother-daughter relationship which is completely relatable. 'They are equally talented designers, but with very different aesthetics, and watching them transform one home a week will be almost as entertaining as the antics that ensue along the way.' Sweet: Miley captioned the pic: 'Sug Bear' as she appeared to be having a blast on the farm with her family Meanwhile, Miley's 27-year-old fiancé, Liam Hemsworth, was enjoying his own family getaway as he was spotted checking out the waves in Malibu on Saturday with his brother Luke, 36. The couple - who fell in love on the 2009 set of The Last Song - were recently spotted enjoying a cozy Valentine's Day date on Tuesday. Miley and Liam confirmed their on/off engagement was back on last March following a two-year split. Going strong: Meanwhile, the singer is going steady with her 27-year-old fiancé, Liam Hemsworth, as the two were spotted enjoying a casual dinner on Valentine's Day The Grammy and Golden Globe nominee is currently working on her sixth album. She will sit out the 12th season of NBC's The Voice after two series in the judges chair, but has vowed to return to coach the 13th season. Liam is currently enjoying an acting hiatus following the dismal critical response from last year's western The Duel and sequel Independence Day: Resurgence.
